1. *Kap* je pao na moju ruku. (A drop fell on my hand.)
2. Uzmi *kap* vode sa sobom. (Take a bottle of water with you.)
3. *Kap* po *kap*, napunila se čaša. (Drop by drop, the glass filled up.)
4. Stavila sam *kap* ulja u tavu. (I put a drop of oil in the pan.)
5. Izlio je *kap* mleka na sto. (He spilled a drop of milk on the table.)
6. *Kap* kiše se odbija od krova. (The raindrop bounces off the roof.)
7. Nemoj da *kaplje*š po podu, obriši to! (Don't drip on the floor, wipe it!)
8. *Kapi* mi sa nosa, imam alergiju. (My nose is running, I have allergies.)
9. Moram da *kapnem* malo limunovog soka u supu. (I need to add a little lemon juice to the soup.)
10. Vozač se pridržavao ograničenja brzine do *kapućinera*. (The driver adhered to the speed limit until the coffee shop.)